entries.journal_entry_description: A group of mining professionals had a bunker in the mountains of Naboo. A group of criminals have taken over the bunker with their trained animals. Clear them out.
entries.task00_comm_message_text: I got a job for you. Some folk took possession of a base and the owners want it back. The new owners don't seem willing to let them take it back. Help them see reason.
entries.task00_journal_entry_description: Sgt. Snopel sent you a message: I got a job for you. Some folk took possession of a base and the owners want it back. The new owners don't seem willing to let them take it back. Help them see reason.
entries.task00_journal_entry_title: You Received a Message from Sgt. Snopel
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: Head over to the bunker that Sgt. Snopel told you about. He will give you further instructions then.
entries.task03_comm_message_text: Kill the inhabitants and reset the locks. There are 3 terminals inside that need to be reset.
entries.task03_journal_entry_description: Sgt. Snopel sent you another message: Kill the inhabitants and reset the locks. There are 3 terminals inside that need to be reset.
entries.task04_journal_entry_description: Find the three Locking Terminals and reset them. Kill anyone that stands in your way.
entries.task06_comm_message_text: Good work, soldier. I have a contact in Theed that will give you your payment. You did good.
entries.task06_journal_entry_description: Sgt. Snopel sent you a final message: Good work, soldier. I have a contact in Theed that will give you your payment. You did good.
entries.task07_journal_entry_description: Galuf Cardaan will pay you for your service.
entries.task07_journal_entry_title: Talk to Galuf Cardaan in Theed
